{"tid":1125042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係條街上面行，對眼望邊度先唔會比人話？","createTime":"2019-04-25T12:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T12:32:43.000Z","uid":189386,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8abc93b09dd15be6a29b6d55917f42f3536e83f","tid":1125042,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"望天：望唔到街，會比車撞<br />\n望地：冇自信，毒撚<br />\n望空氣：雙目無神<br />\n<br />\n望少女：咸濕死毒撚，死撚開啦屌你<br />\n望呀婆：變態<br />\n望細路：戀童<br />\n望男人：基<br />\n<br />\n一係就求其搵啲死物望：望黎冇乜意義<br />\n<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我發現如果對眼成日轉目標，例如一秒轉一次，會比人感覺好怪，覺得你係變態佬，身有屎<br />\n<br />\n有冇社交達人教下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5115d861e79fa94379ad16a686b618314f4dcb54","tid":1125042,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"街囉 一定要望住人㗎咩"},{"pid":"1f6a2ec39e9291f84f7479897ed7907375134e77","tid":1125042,"uid":152240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"望電話<br />\n<br />\n止帖已完。"},{"pid":"9728cdcc38e896cd8ba490a0ca3f99ddc1eb0052","tid":1125042,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1f6a2ec39e9291f84f7479897ed7907375134e77","tid":1125042,"uid":152240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"望電話<br />\n<br />\n止帖已完。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"係 講少左<br />\n望電話：望到頭暈 比車撞"},{"pid":"cb35a6e80e44b5e0e4fe3f7945544f002a67c862","tid":1125042,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"Btw乜真係有人會望下人就比人話㗎咩<br />\n如果真 咁樓豬應該幾樣衰"},{"pid":"9caef669113954663a951d0850a77930f56702fb","tid":1125042,"uid":149959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"最靚嗰條女"},{"pid":"8a128cceac0c59a256f3bd7a4f700f0d68bb8dd1","tid":1125042,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor